Theme notes:
https://github.com/IronSummitMedia/startbootstrap-clean-blog-jekyll - chosen
https://github.com/brianmaierjr/long-haul - alternative

Do a cname: https://help.github.com/articles/setting-up-a-custom-domain-with-github-pages/

# Must be run from base dir

Mac:
docker run -e BUNDLE_CACHE=1 --rm --label=jekyll --volume=$(pwd):/srv/jekyll -it -p $(boot2docker ip):4000:4000 jekyll/jekyll jekyll s --force_polling --unpublished --future

Linux:
docker run -e BUNDLE_CACHE=1 --privileged --rm --label=jekyll --volume=$(pwd):/srv/jekyll -it -p 4000:4000 jekyll/jekyll jekyll s --force_polling --unpublished --future
